short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: How to Set Your Hourly Rate as a Contract Developer

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
As a contractor, you need to be realistic about the number of workdays you actually have in a month and year. Billable helps you estimate an hourly rate.
